cach-chap-tien-ga-choi\/#Theo_do_kho_cua_tran_da_ga\" >Theo \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi\/\">c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/a> r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Sv368<\/a> s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i chi ti\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chia s\u1ebb c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khai_niem_cach_chap_tien_ga_choi_la_gi\"><\/span><b>Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trang c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea tham gia c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed v\u1eadn may. <\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea7m am hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0, ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t b\u00ean ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa hai chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4263\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4263\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4263 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-1.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-1.jpg?v=1736159240 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-1-300x150.jpg?v=1736159240 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-1-768x384.jpg?v=1736159240 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4263\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_chap_tien_ga_choi_hien_nay\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hinh_thuc_chap_tien_theo_ty_le\"><\/span><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c c\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0. Khi hai chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t b\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, n\u1ebfu g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5p n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eefa hai chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_chap_tien_ga_choi_theo_co_dinh\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi theo c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra khi m\u1ed9t s\u01b0 k\u00ea \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c c\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1edbi g\u00e0. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i mu\u1ed1n tham gia m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4264\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4264\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4264 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-2.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-2.jpg?v=1736159263 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-2-300x150.jpg?v=1736159263 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-2-768x384.jpg?v=1736159263 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4264\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi theo c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chap_tien_duoc_linh_hoat\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c linh ho\u1ea1t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i linh ho\u1ea1t theo di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Khi m\u1ed9t b\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ho\u1eb7c khi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4265\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4265\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4265 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-3.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-3.jpg?v=1736159287 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-3-300x150.jpg?v=1736159287 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-3-768x384.jpg?v=1736159287 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4265\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi hi\u1ec7n nay<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_tinh_tien_chap_ga_choi_hieu_qua\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, bao g\u1ed3m s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eefa hai chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u01b0\u1ee3c do c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thuc_hien_tinh_toan_theo_suc_manh_ga_choi\"><\/span><b>Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n theo s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, s\u01b0 k\u00ea c\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea tham gia. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 chi\u1ec1u cao, c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e9 \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n. N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5p. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Theo_do_kho_cua_tran_da_ga\"><\/span><b>Theo \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc khi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu hai b\u00ean ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c th\u00ec t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, s\u01b0 k\u00ea c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ti\u1ec1n c\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4266\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4266\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4266 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-4.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-4.jpg?v=1736159311 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-4-300x150.jpg?v=1736159311 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-chap-tien-ga-choi-4-768x384.jpg?v=1736159311 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4266\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn anh em th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Ch\u00fac anh em tham gia ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi t\u1ea1i Sv368 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Sv368 s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i chi ti\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chia s\u1ebb c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4265,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4262","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","h